{"tid":1657482,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【831太子站】前法庭書記睹警毆乘客疑患PTSD　向盧偉聰索償押後明年再訊","createTime":"2019-10-16T06:08:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T06:20:40.000Z","uid":51271,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"54b8edb58678df4bd3f878a11afe148e974d9922","tid":1657482,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T06:08:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20191016/s00001/1571200873808/%e3%80%90831%e5%a4%aa%e5%ad%90%e7%ab%99%e3%80%91%e5%89%8d%e6%b3%95%e5%ba%ad%e6%9b%b8%e8%a8%98%e7%9d%b9%e8%ad%a6%e6%af%86%e4%b9%98%e5%ae%a2%e7%96%91%e6%82%a3ptsd-%e5%90%91%e7%9b%a7%e5%81%89%e8%81%b0%e7%b4%a2%e5%84%9f%e6%8a%bc%e5%be%8c%e6%98%8e%e5%b9%b4%e5%86%8d%e8%a8%8a\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20191016%2Fs00001%2F1571200873808%2F%25e3%2580%2590831%25e5%25a4%25aa%25e5%25ad%2590%25e7%25ab%2599%25e3%2580%2591%25e5%2589%258d%25e6%25b3%2595%25e5%25ba%25ad%25e6%259b%25b8%25e8%25a8%2598%25e7%259d%25b9%25e8%25ad%25a6%25e6%25af%2586%25e4%25b9%2598%25e5%25ae%25a2%25e7%2596%2591%25e6%2582%25a3ptsd-%25e5%2590%2591%25e7%259b%25a7%25e5%2581%2589%25e8%2581%25b0%25e7%25b4%25a2%25e5%2584%259f%25e6%258a%25bc%25e5%25be%258c%25e6%2598%258e%25e5%25b9%25b4%25e5%2586%258d%25e8%25a8%258a&d=TC1Ad7l9MtPLjBCdpR1LVitC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlEes%3D&h=926f86a4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20191016%2Fs00001%2F1571200873808%2F%25e3%2580%2590831%25e5%25a4%25aa%25e5%25ad%2590%25e7%25ab%2599%25e3%2580%2591%25e5%2589%258d%25e6%25b3%2595%25e5%25ba%25ad%25e6%259b%25b8%25e8%25a8%2598%25e7%259d%25b9%25e8%25ad%25a6%25e6%25af%2586%25e4%25b9%2598%25e5%25ae%25a2%25e7%2596%2591%25e6%2582%25a3ptsd-%25e5%2590%2591%25e7%259b%25a7%25e5%2581%2589%25e8%2581%25b0%25e7%25b4%25a2%25e5%2584%259f%25e6%258a%25bc%25e5%25be%258c%25e6%2598%258e%25e5%25b9%25b4%25e5%2586%258d%25e8%25a8%258a&h=9c1e7162\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20191016/s00001/1571200873808/%e3%80%90831%e5%a4%aa%e5%ad%90%e7%ab%99%e3%80%91%e5%89%8d%e6%b3%95%e5%ba%ad%e6%9b%b8%e8%a8%98%e7%9d%b9%e8%ad%a6%e6%af%86%e4%b9%98%e5%ae%a2%e7%96%91%e6%82%a3ptsd-%e5%90%91%e7%9b%a7%e5%81%89%e8%81%b0%e7%b4%a2%e5%84%9f%e6%8a%bc%e5%be%8c%e6%98%8e%e5%b9%b4%e5%86%8d%e8%a8%8a</a><br />\n<br />\n警方速龍小隊及防暴警在8月31日晚進入港鐵太子站，涉嫌用警棍打車廂乘客和示威者。前合約法庭書記從電視直播目睹過程，懷疑患上創傷後壓力症候群（PTSD），他早前入稟要求警務處長為其精神創傷賠償5000元。案件今（16日）於小額錢債審裁處提訊，案件將押後至明年1月3日再訊。<br />\n<br />\n申索人譚志輝，被告為警務處長盧偉聰。警務處一方在庭上表示，譚志輝並非太子站當事人的父母或子女，並無親密關係，故要求法庭剔除相關申請。惟譚志輝否認，他表示自己雖不認識當事人，但大家同是香港人，從示威活動中建立了親密情感。<br />\n<br />\n審裁官決定將案件押後至明年1月3日再訊，屆時將處理相關法律爭議。<br />\n<br />\n申索書指出，警察8月31日於港鐵太子站以警棍打沒有威脅的乘客，無視《警察通例》中「使用最低程度武力」指引，涉干犯民事法的「疏忽」侵權行為。申索書又指出，申索人及市民從直播目睹上述「恐襲式」場面，令申索人感焦慮不安，懷疑自己患上創傷後壓力症候群，要求警務處長為他精神創傷賠償共5000元。"},{"pid":"c00296aa120334a0be78ac7f2ed82743ad25676c","tid":1657482,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T06:08:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MHn4YGm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMHn4YGm.jpg&h=a9bf801a&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"c4a22e93a40356cf160dd88cca9eeb821cddf150","tid":1657482,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T06:10:19.000Z","msg":"Nice"},{"pid":"da1c8dace123729030b8a879c96de79656a184b8","tid":1657482,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T06:10:47.000Z","msg":"和理非抗爭!"},{"pid":"3fd94fe260f55286caa681701fa62172a8348663","tid":1657482,"uid":165683,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T06:11:27.000Z","msg":"譚志輝並非太子站當事人的父母或子女，並無親密關係，故要求法庭剔除相關申請。惟譚志輝否認，他表示自己雖不認識當事人，但大家同是香港人，從示威活動中建立了親密情感。"},{"pid":"5f058490a01cf56ddb5ab6c7e9f81b803966c81b","tid":1657482,"uid":2607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T06:11:27.000Z","msg":"Nice"},{"pid":"e796010d2e237cb2a385449090abfa88a8a868b0","tid":1657482,"uid":69741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T06:12:30.000Z","msg":"押到出年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e722eeb2d731291c09d6a291025ce9361f0bc6b8","tid":1657482,"uid":61882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T06:15:56.000Z","msg":"有冇計叫譚生出篇教學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0eab9f0233fe22a96a37585c096b67dd116d4389","tid":1657482,"uid":286792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T06:20:40.000Z","msg":"推"}]}